Kemmer

Few Days ago i went to Erics house and we went Jet Skiing then the Campbells showed up and i took Eric and Scotty on the jet Ski and only flipped us once. Then on Tuesday i had Heather over to go tubing and woah was that fun the waves were HUGE. then we had pizza and almost made ourselves sick because we ate too much. Then on Wed. i had Monica over and we went fishing and tubing.. thwn i drove the Jet Ski and we tried to run over a bird on the water. That was pretty fun. Then Yesterday i didnt really do anything until around 9 Heather called saying she was having a little get together so i rhode my bike over there and when i got there her sister Amy was moving this big trash bag which was really heavy so it broke obviously knowing me i looked what was in there and it was a TON of new books she was throwing away so heather and i sat down on the ground and started reading the books...then we went inside and i helped Amy move a big shelf out of her room..then Heather me Rachael Larissa Paige and someone else went swimming it was so fun! then my mom came to get me at 11:15 and i went home and watching Finding Nemo before i went to bed. now i'm writing all this and its getting kinda boreing so i'm gunna go fishing again and go get my Bike and Towel that i left at Heathers

Well its been a while since i've updated....

Nothing much has happend..accept my computer broke down about the time of my soccer party which was like 4 weeks ago.so i havent been online since last night.which was my first time.(blah blah)..just got home from Vacataion yesterday morning at 2:30 AM..that was fun...then yesterday unpacked most of the day and helped my nextdoor neighbor dig holes in the sand....it was pretty fun i guess....then last night i went to Carolyns and Taylors party..that was fun..accept i didnt really know many kids there but i found out they kinda knew me from Volleyball and that kind of stuff....then i heard stories of how people broke her fence...and Sam K's Salsa songs.....then Sam K and i sang stories about Stars..that was the best song ever!.....Cleaning my room all day today |: it needs it tho.....then tonight going to Tylers Party..that should be fun........I'll be updating again later today...if i feel like it

Kemmer...

Soccer Ended on Sunday..we had a tourney in Petoskey and went 1-1-1..we could have won that last game but none of the ogals went in...but anywho...after the game Tobin,Kelli,Laural,Ali,Monica and I all went to Tobins cabin and went Tubing!! that was the most fun i have had all summer...having 6 ppl on a tube and then everyone falling off accept aly..oh my goodness!..it was a lot of fun being on that team....we were together ever since U10..and we were the first girls team ever to be around and to win a tournment...so many memos with you girls....wow..i'm gunna miss you all soooo much...were gunna have to get together sometime to play a game aginst the boys team again!!
